                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-1-6">6. What next after PMP certification?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-1-6" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Once you have mastered PMP, you can consider the certifications below:&nbsp;</p>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>PMI Agile Certified Practitioner (PMI-ACP®)&nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>PMI Risk Management Professional (PMI-RMP®)&nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>PMI Scheduling Professional (PMI-SP®)&nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>PMI Professional in Business Analysis (PMI-PBA®)&nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>Portfolio Management Professional (PfMP®)&nbsp;</li>
