            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>Here is a step-by-step process for filling out the PMP application:</p><ul><li>Navigate to the form by visiting the <a href=\"https://www.pmi.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">PMI website</a>.</li><li>On the topmost bar, under the ‘Certification’ option, click ‘Apply Now’.</li><li>You will be asked to log in to your account. If you don’t have one, click on ‘Create an account’.</li><li>Enter the information including your personal details, work details, etc. Once the account is created, visit the <a href=\"https://idp.pmi.org/account/login?returnUrl=%2Fconnect%2Fauthorize%2Fcallback%3Fclient_id%3Dsitecore_55d31c97bc7e47bdb07e2a550340813c%26redirect_uri%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.pmi.org%252Fsignin-identityserver%26response_mode%3Dform_post%26response_type%3Dcode%26scope%3Dopenid%2520profile%2520email%2520CERTAPI%2520CERTPROFILEAPI%26state%3DOpenIdConnect.AuthenticationProperties%253DKwAa8kU5aY37hGLfnFmAP0DBllLauy6WCCwgafqW-AXOMivw5gzKUp9DLcNPLQ2eajRb582WH7tvKP5rPKTCHRYLdxE7C-TP6BxfGWJaR8DddIRAb5Ls3ZKJIBZYlvYIPGijAEUNQH2_PLwdmat4wDZirbTObogRaYYgsIbMi8ggY0dl_p_QRYV2l5cDalCMK1HOW7W4FVaxl4XChB1oKbdxjwDcMJ7rV7WH0QYg-4uqJt0BGqtokNSQy1u2h32CQIqYw8H-WxDuHFpL8Jr3UTF0-W38hs5aYNNxH77SIli6cnIsfCsxrCT3tiUN9jmEeBekLw%26nonce%3D637299689691334212.NzA1ZjQ3OTktMjM3My00ODYyLWE3MTMtZTAzMTUxNjAxY2RmOGMwMjJjYjMtZjliNS00Y2Y0LWJiNDItZDVlZDdmYmVjZDk3%26x-client-SKU%3DID_NET451%26x-client-ver%3D5.2.2.0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">link</a> and click ‘Apply for PMP Credential’.</li><li>You will be redirected to the form. There are several steps where you will have to include your contact address, contact information, attained education, Project Management education, experience, optional information (primary referral source), etc.</li><li>You can pay for the certification exam after you receive approval of your PMP application from PMI.</li></ul>"
            }
        }, {
