        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "How long does it take for PMI to approve the PMP application?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>Once you have submitted your application, PMI will take 5 business days or a week to approve your application. If your application is approved, you will receive the email confirmation. However, if you are audited, the approval might take longer. Please note that your application getting selected for an audit is a purely random process.</p>"
