            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>The PMP examination is comprised of 200 multiple-choice questions and has to be completed in 4 hours. Of the 200 questions, 25 are considered pretest questions and do not affect the score.</p><p>Please check the PMP handbook for complete details at this link: <a href=\"#"
                target = \"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">PMP handbook</a>.</p>"
