                "text": "<p>Reading the best books is important to pass the PMP exam.</p><p>Below is the list of books that can help you prepare for PMP exam:</p><ol><li>The latest edition of the PMBOK® Guide </li><li>Rita Mulcahy’s PMP Exam Prep </li><li>Head First PMP by Jennifer Greene </li><li>PMP Exam simplified by Eileen Ellis </li><li>The Velociteach All-In-One PMP Exam Prep Kit.</li></ol>"
